WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.000
From this warehouse, we send more than 5,000 international shipments every day.

2
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:32.000
<v Erkan Dulkadir>Last year we had 367,000 shipments, with 180% growth compared to the year before — and we're aiming to grow even more this year, thanks to Zineps.

3
00:00:50.000 --> 00:01:16.000
<v Burak>Our operational side is stronger and faster than ever. We went live within a week, ran a test period, and then fully switched over. The best part is how quickly we can add new carriers and enter new markets — and we get better shipping terms, so we can serve our customers even better.
